{"tid":925642,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"🎉樓爆勁減一成🎊港島業主哭求賣樓微賺459萬離場","createTime":"2018-12-03T01:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T04:55:56.000Z","uid":43146,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a415d1f0c3b36cd1b5b20fb09913223029754a","tid":925642,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:34:41.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 中原地產表示，分行促成成交單位為北角富雅花園3座金楓閣中層C室，實用面積451平方呎，建築面積513平方呎，2房間隔。業主以696萬元將單位易手，折合平均實用呎價15432元。<br />\n<br />\n買家為區內客，睇樓約一個月，見該單位比早前有一成多折讓，隨即入市。原業主於1996年12月以236.5萬元買入單位，持貨22年，賬面獲利459.5萬元，單位升值接近2倍。"},{"pid":"3085bc1d7026edae974e836dec610a98ea58891c","tid":925642,"uid":164980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:42:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58326a81ae1424d8d1e70ab0010484ce154ada67","tid":925642,"uid":30293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:43:25.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"f8f38691d6d4c5515ba832d96ddc5b06dfcaaf75","tid":925642,"uid":186543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:43:50.000Z","msg":"爽，賺少咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93b1f230f238c0c724684241246cf7c9c0e21f0","tid":925642,"uid":7905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"微賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n微電影咩屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaccace545bf1d5f058f3ae6e4bf98cecbbdf51f","tid":925642,"uid":125261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3085bc1d7026edae974e836dec610a98ea58891c","tid":925642,"uid":164980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:42:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T01:47:22.000Z","msg":"私樓黎架<br />\n大埔有個同名屋苑就係居屋"},{"pid":"4ab3e385f58994